beer.beer_description: This All Hop NEIPA is made entirely from malt, hops, water yeast and some oats. No fruit juice or concentrate have been added. A subtle hazy and cloudiness, this IPA oozes of fruit flavours including Mango, pineapple, strawberries and citrus. A stong yet ultimately refreshing NEIPA it would have been served only in the First Class on Zeppelin flights between Berlin and Tokyo, Pity is was not invented back then. The Pony says, let the Zeppelin roar.
